parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the instrument cluster can cause the dashboard lights to go on and off, making it difficult for the driver to monitor the vehicle's speed and other essential functions, which can lead to accidents or fines.
symptoms: Dashboard lights go on and off
lights do not come on at all
inability to see speedometer at night.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The stalling of the engine can cause the vehicle to lose power and come to a sudden stop, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Engine stalls while driving
engine will not crank
starter will not turn engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the window regulator can cause the window to become inoperable and fall inside the door, which can obstruct the driver's view and cause accidents.
symptoms: Window becomes inoperable
window falls inside the door without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the horn can cause it to blow unexpectedly, which can startle other drivers and pedestrians, leading to accidents or road rage incidents.
symptoms: Horn starts to blow at all hours
horn goes off in traffic.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause smoke to come from the interior lights, which can lead to fires or electrical shocks.
symptoms: Smoke coming from interior lights.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the ignition switch can cause the airbags to not deploy in the event of an accident, which can lead to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Ignition does not stay in position
ignition can move to ACC or ON position when car is started.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the safety sensors can cause the vehicle to lose power and stall, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Safety sensors and warning lights go off
vehicle loses power and stalls
starter grinds and has a mind of its own.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the PCM can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or experience erratic behavior, which can lead to accidents, especially when driving at high speeds.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power
stalls
or experiences erratic behavior
the check engine light illuminates
the vehicle is unable to idle for a long period
the vehicle has difficulty accelerating
the instrument cluster lights flash erratically
the vehicle has reduced power
and the power steering becomes difficult to operate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose motive power, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses motive power
the transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear
the vehicle stalls or shuts off
and the vehicle has difficulty accelerating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the battery can cause the vehicle to experience a complete loss of power, making it difficult or impossible to start the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle experiences a complete loss of power
the battery drains excessively
the vehicle is unable to start
and the battery needs to be replaced frequently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can lead to the failure of airbags to deploy in the event of an accident, potentially resulting in serious injury or fatalities. Additionally, unexpected airbag deployment can cause accidents, injuries, or distractions while driving.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
airbags deploy unexpectedly
airbags fail to deploy in the event of an accident
beeping or other warning sounds.
